        "Radiography": {
          "text": "Pneumatosis on XR is hallmark\nGet\nKUB\nin supine position and left lat decubitus\nUltrasound\nPseudo-kidney sign - bowel wall with hyperechoic center and hypoechoic rim\nAssess for gas bubbles in liver and portal veins",
